text: Bulak-Bashy or Bulak-Bashi may refer to the following places in Kyrgyzstan: *Bulak-Bashy, Leilek, a village in the Leilek District, Batken Region *Bulak- Bashy, Batken, a village in the city of Batken, Batken Region *Bulak-Bashy, Jalal-Abad, a village in the Ala-Buka District, Jalal-Abad Region
title: Bulak-Bashy
